content:
I'm getting the following error on my SD which is curious since I used the SD created by ig.pub minus the narrative and snapshot. What is is the rule beside they need to be unique. P.s. this is a dstu2 artifact

StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[2].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:authorize' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[3].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:authorize.url' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[4].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:authorize.valueUri' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[5].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:token' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[6].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:token.url' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[7].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:token.valueUri' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[8].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:register' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[9].id  error   id value 'Extension.extension:register.url' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[10].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:register.valueUri' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[11].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:manage' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[12].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:manage.url' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[13].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:manage.valueUri' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[14].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:introspect' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[15].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:introspect.url' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[16].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:introspect.valueUri' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[17].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:revoke' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[18].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:revoke.url' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[19].id error   id value 'Extension.extension:revoke.valueUri' is not valid
StructureDefinition/oauth-uris: StructureDefinition.differential.element[21].id error   id value 'Extension.value[x]' is not valid
hmm interesting. That's a STU2 problem. The data type of Element.id in R2 is id, and the pattern used for IDs in subsquent versions is not a valid id...
